ide to over<a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.localiq.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteBestOnlineMarketingTips.html?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_130marketingtips_Download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> 130 of the best online marketing tips for more traffic, leads, and sales<\/a>!<\/p>\n<div id=\"holiday-advertising-google\"><\/div>\n<h3>Google Ads<\/h3>\n<p>To kick off our list of <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/free-holiday-marketing-resources\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">holiday advertising resources<\/a>, we\u2019re going with one from a platform that\u2019s extremely popular any time of year: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/03\/21\/how-to-run-google-ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Ads<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>This past August, Google <a href=\"https:\/\/business.google.com\/us\/think\/consumer-insights\/modern-consumer-holiday-marketing-strategy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">released an article<\/a> titled \u201cHoliday shopping: Unlocking the modern consumer\u2019s new value equation.\u201d This resource is essentially a list of ways Google recommends businesses build and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/google-ads-holiday-strategies\">optimize holiday ad campaigns<\/a> using Google\u2019s insights on how consumers are making purchasing decisions this season. If you\u2019re trying to get ahead of competitors this season, it also signals which ideas revolve around AI-powered Google Ads features.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-resource-example.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - google ads holiday resource screenshot\" width=\"900\" height=\"460\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-95273 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-resource-example.webp 900w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-resource-example-480x245.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Here are the main takeaways:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Prioritize customer data and insights for a better performance. <\/strong>According to Google, <a href=\"https:\/\/support.google.com\/google-ads\/answer\/15302774\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">72%<\/a> of ecommerce businesses report that advanced consumer insights are helpful in their holiday planning, so advertisers should focus on this in their account. For example, you can try the customer acquisition goal in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/07\/05\/performance-max-tips\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Performance Max<\/a> or Search campaigns for clearer tracking and better bidding optimization.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Use updated holiday creative to increase sales during the holiday season.<\/strong> Google\u2019s AI can automatically generate assets in Product Studio and beyond, allowing you to quickly create and edit ad images, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2019\/02\/26\/product-photography\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">product photos<\/a>, and more.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Be prepared for seasonal shifts in performance. <\/strong>If you use the recommendations section of Google Ads and\/or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/12\/19\/google-ads-automated-bidding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Ads smart bidding<\/a> but expect your performance to fluctuate (throwing off what Google\u2019s machine learning would typically recommend), you can apply <a href=\"https:\/\/support.google.com\/google-ads\/answer\/9352512\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">seasonality adjustments<\/a> for more tailored AI optimization from Google.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Consider how customers are moving through your buyer&#8217;s journey.<\/strong> Google&#8217;s research found that holiday shoppers are looking at three key factors when making purchasing decisions: a product or service&#8217;s cost, a product or service&#8217;s credibility, and how convenient it is to purchase that product or service. Be sure to hit on your brand&#8217;s unique value, reputation, and convenience factors like free shipping or nearby locations, in your holiday ads.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-buyers-journey.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - google holiday customer consideration journey\" width=\"742\" height=\"523\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-95296 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-buyers-journey.webp 742w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-google-ads-buyers-journey-480x338.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 742px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udea8<strong>Are your current PPC campaigns ready for the holidays?<\/strong> Find out with our Free <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/google-adwords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_PPC_AWGrader_AWGrader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Ads Grader<\/a>!<\/p>\n<div id=\"holiday-advertising-microsoft\"><\/div>\n<h3>Microsoft Ads<\/h3>\n<p>Similarly to Google Ads, Microsoft Ads released a <a href=\"https:\/\/about.ads.microsoft.com\/content\/dam\/sites\/msa-about\/global\/common\/content-lib\/pdf\/the-advertisers-holiday-performance-playbook.pdf?s_cid=gl-ob-imoth-imoth-src_wpage-sub_ip-cam_holidayguidelp-flx_downloadguide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">holiday advertising playbook<\/a> in September. Microsoft Ads\u2019 top recommendations for this holiday season are:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Use multiple ad formats to gain exposure fast.<\/strong> Microsoft reports that users spend more when exposed to more unique ad formats. Advertisers should try CTV ads, display ads, videos, and native ads as early as possible to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2015\/07\/10\/brand-awareness\">generate brand awareness<\/a> and consideration throughout the season.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Advertisers should focus their efforts on the Cyber 5. <\/strong>Microsoft Ads discusses the importance of <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/types-of-advertising\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">advertising<\/a> heavily during the \u201cCyber 5,\u201d also known as the timeframe between Thanksgiving and Cyber Monday that includes Black Friday, Giving Tuesday, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/small-business-saturday-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Small Business Saturday<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Like the Google holiday ads article, Microsoft Ads also encourages advertisers to take advantage of its AI-powered ad solutions to generate ad assets and optimize campaign bidding and targeting. The resource finishes out with a handy holiday checklist, too.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-microsoft.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - microsoft ads holiday guide\" width=\"551\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86311 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-microsoft.webp 551w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-microsoft-480x523.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 551px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"holiday-meta-ads\"><\/div>\n<h3>Meta Ads<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/2024-facebook-ads-trends\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Meta Ads<\/a> offers a free-to-download <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/business\/holiday-marketing-guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">guide on holiday advertising<\/a> that\u2019s broken out into four steps, which are:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Plan:<\/strong> To get ready for the holidays, Meta advertisers should focus on <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/marketing-budget\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">setting a budget<\/a>, optimizing for the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/10\/06\/facebook-conversions-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Conversions API<\/a>, and simplifying their account structure.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Experiment: <\/strong>Meta Ads recommends that businesses A\/B test <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/meta-advantage-plus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">using Meta Advantage+ features<\/a>, and source inspiration from other successful brands to brainstorm experiments.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Push:<\/strong> Use recommended best practices from Meta Ads to efficiently measure and progress holiday campaign performance.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Sustain:<\/strong> Meta reports that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/facebook-ads-benchmarks-2024\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook ad costs<\/a> are typically lower in the new year. By keeping holiday campaigns active for longer, advertisers can maintain success at a cheaper cost.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>The guide also covers strategies for customer engagement and <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/lead-generation-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lead generation<\/a> during the holiday season using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/09\/26\/facebook-lead-ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook Lead Ads<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-facebook.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - meta ads holiday playbook\" width=\"548\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86310 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-facebook.webp 548w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-facebook-480x526.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 548px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udca1<strong>See<\/strong><strong> how much your seasonal Facebook campaigns might cost<\/strong> using our free <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/resources\/facebook-benchmarks?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_FBAdsBenchmarks2024_Download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook Ads benchmarks report<\/a>!<\/p>\n<div id=\"yelp-holiday-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h3>Yelp Ads<\/h3>\n<p>While Yelp doesn\u2019t have a downloadable guide for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/11\/05\/december-marketing-ideas\">seasonal marketing<\/a>, it does offer a comprehensive article full of holiday tips for <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/yelp-ads\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Yelp advertising<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Here are some of the recommended best practices for holiday Yelp ads:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Focus on the quality of your Yelp ads (from your audience\u2019s perspective). <\/strong>Yelp puts an emphasis on ensuring your holiday ads are genuinely helpful to your target audience. This will help your ads stand out during such a busy season. For example, you want your ad text to be relevant and personalized.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Make it as easy as possible for customers to convert from your Yelp ads.<\/strong> To solve any logistical problems for your customers during this time of year, you could mention options like \u201cbuy online and pickup in-store\u201d or \u201cbuy now, pay later.\u201d<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>In addition to Yelp\u2019s holiday article, the platform offers a free on-demand webinar covering <a href=\"https:\/\/brands.yelp.com\/webinars\/yelp-advertising-for-the-holiday-season\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Yelp advertising for the holiday season<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-yelp.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - yelp ads holiday article\" width=\"741\" height=\"518\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86307 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-yelp.webp 741w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-yelp-480x336.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 741px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"tiktok-holiday-advertising\"><\/div>\n<h3>TikTok Advertising<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/08\/11\/advertising-on-tiktok\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TikTok<\/a> publishes a holiday advertising guide every year, and <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.tiktok.com\/business\/en-US\/holiday?ab_version=experiment_1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this year\u2019s<\/a> covers:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>The importance of using holiday hashtags<\/strong>. The platform recommends using these top seven <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/04\/07\/tiktok-hashtags\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TikTok hashtags<\/a> to increase holiday visibility: #thanksgiving, #blackfriday, #cybermonday, #christmas, #hanukkah, #kwanzaa, #nochebuena.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Getting ahead of your holiday marketing plan is crucial for <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/08\/23\/tiktok-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>TikTok campaign success<\/strong><\/a><strong>. <\/strong>TikTok recommends creating content for before, during, <em>and <\/em>after the holiday buzz.<\/li>\n<li><strong>There\u2019s a three-part formula for the perfect holiday TikTok.<\/strong> TikTok encourages businesses to create videos that include a killer hook within the first three to five seconds, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/unique-selling-proposition\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">unique selling points<\/a>, and one <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/powerful-call-to-action-phrases\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">clear CTA<\/a> (and consider <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/holiday-influencer-marketing\">partnering with an influencer<\/a>).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>For advertisers just starting this season, the guide also includes some insight into the ad campaign <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2020\/07\/22\/tiktok-ads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">buildout process in TikTok Ads<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-tiktok.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - tiktok ads\" width=\"425\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86309 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-tiktok.webp 425w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-tiktok-213x300.webp 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"holiday-advertising-spotify\"><\/div>\n<h3>Spotify Ads<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/seasonal-marketing\/holiday-advertising\/?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=us-en-dynamic-search-ads&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwmaO4BhAhEiwA5p4YLxFV7jm-i2fBI_MR90FSDsgXMZNhKPrNmWy_pE2fv9_2GD5hp-MlXhoCeXAQAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The latest holiday ads resource<\/a> from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/07\/13\/spotify-advertising\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Spotify Ads<\/a> might not be as long as some of the others on our list, but it still covers a ton of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/11\/27\/holiday-marketing-stats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">holiday marketing stats<\/a> you can use to get ahead this season.<\/p>\n<p>For example, did you know that festive playlist streaming increases by <a href=\"https:\/\/ads.spotify.com\/en-US\/seasonal-marketing\/holiday-advertising\/?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=us-en-dynamic-search-ads&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwmaO4BhAhEiwA5p4YLxFV7jm-i2fBI_MR90FSDsgXMZNhKPrNmWy_pE2fv9_2GD5hp-MlXhoCeXAQAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">59%<\/a> in November and 85% in December? That means a larger potential audience is available for your business to tap into this time of year.<\/p>\n<p>Here are some of the other quick tips from Spotify for seasonal ads:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Combine different ad formats for the perfect Spotify holiday campaign strategy.<\/strong> Spotify recommends using multiple ad formats to ensure your holiday ads are seen and heard at different moments throughout the day.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Use first-party data to build a Spotify audience you can count on this season.<\/strong> Whether you deliver a festive message via audio or video (or both) you can pair Spotify with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/04\/12\/first-party-data\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">your business\u2019s first-party data<\/a> to help your ads reach audiences when they\u2019re most engaged.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-spotify.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - spotify ads\" width=\"900\" height=\"483\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86308 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-spotify.webp 900w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-spotify-480x258.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"amazon-holiday-ads\"><\/div>\n<h3>Amazon Ads<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/advertising.amazon.com\/events\/holidays\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The holiday advertising resource<\/a> on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/01\/27\/top-reasons-to-sell-on-amazon-2021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Amazon Ads<\/a> site is a compilation of articles created to help brands grow during the platform\u2019s busiest season. It includes:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/marketing-calendar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>seasonal marketing calendar<\/strong><\/a><strong> for key Amazon holiday dates.<\/strong> You\u2019ll want to ensure you have ads running during Amazon\u2019s high-volume shopping days like Diwali and New Year\u2019s.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Case studies and insights from thought leaders.<\/strong> Amazon refers to six different successful holiday ad campaigns businesses can learn from. It also includes a link to insights from a marketing expert regarding the importance of incorporating Amazon Ads into a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/06\/22\/cross-channel-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cross-channel marketing strategy<\/a> for maximized holiday success.<\/li>\n<li><strong>A holiday marketing FAQ section.<\/strong> Amazon provides answers to key holiday advertising questions like \u201cwhen is the holiday season?\u201d and \u201cwhat are the key seasonal and cultural events marketers should prioritize?\u201d<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-amazon.webp\" alt=\"holiday advertising - amazon ads\" width=\"962\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-86306 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-amazon.webp 962w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/holiday-advertising-amazon-480x299.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 962px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Use these resources for a winning holiday advertising game plan<\/h2>\n<p>No matter which <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/06\/26\/marketing-channels\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">marketing channels<\/a> you decide to leverage this holiday season, there are resources available to help you navigate the rush of festivities.<\/p>\n<p>These holiday advertising playbooks all have one theme in common: consumer engagement has been proven to increase during the holiday months. So, regardless of whether you\u2019re advertising sales or services, you\u2019re more likely to see campaign success when you enable campaigns over the holidays and all <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/winter-content-ideas\">winter<\/a>. For more help with your seasonal marketing, see how <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/marketing-services?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Demo_Blog_Demo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our solutions<\/a> can empower you to make the most out of your holiday campaigns.<\/p>\n<p><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"hippowiz-ass-injected\" value=\"true\" \/><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"hvmessage-toextension-listener\" value=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Make a winning game plan for your business this season with this complete holiday advertising playbook featuring resources from top platforms. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":69,"featured_media":86321,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[96],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-86301","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-seasonal-marketing"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>The Ul